7#include <algorithm>
8#include <unordered_map>
9
10#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect.h"
11#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/AstHelpers.h"
12#include "compiler/translator/TranslatorMetalDirect/ReduceInterfaceBlocks.h"
13#include "compiler/translator/tree_ops/SeparateDeclarations.h"
14#include "compiler/translator/tree_util/IntermRebuild.h"
15
16using namespace sh;
17
18////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
19
20namespace
21{
22
23
24class Reducer : public TIntermRebuild
25{
26 std::unordered_map<const TInterfaceBlock *, const TVariable *>
27 mLiftedMap;
28 std::unordered_map<const TVariable *, const TVariable *> mInstanceMap;
29 IdGen & mIdGen;
30 public:
31 Reducer(TCompiler &compiler, IdGen & idGen) : TIntermRebuild(compiler, true, false),
32 mIdGen(idGen)
33 {
34
35 }
36
37 PreResult visitDeclarationPre(TIntermDeclaration &declNode) override
38 {
39 ASSERT(declNode.getChildCount() == 1);
40 TIntermNode &node = *declNode.getChildNode(0);
41
42 if (TIntermSymbol *symbolNode = node.getAsSymbolNode())
43 {
44 const TVariable &var = symbolNode->variable();
45 const TType &type = var.getType();
46 const SymbolType symbolType = var.symbolType();
47 if (const TInterfaceBlock *interfaceBlock = type.getInterfaceBlock())
48 {
49 if (symbolType == SymbolType::Empty)
50 {
51 //Create instance variable
52 auto &structure =
53 *new TStructure(&mSymbolTable, interfaceBlock->name(),
54 &interfaceBlock->fields(), interfaceBlock->symbolType());
55 auto &structVar = CreateStructTypeVariable(mSymbolTable, structure);
56
57 auto &instanceVar =
58 CreateInstanceVariable(mSymbolTable, structure, mIdGen.createNewName(interfaceBlock->name()),
59 TQualifier::EvqBuffer, &type.getArraySizes());
60 mLiftedMap[interfaceBlock] = &instanceVar;
61
62 TIntermNode *replacements[] = {
63 new TIntermDeclaration{new TIntermSymbol(&structVar)},
64 new TIntermDeclaration{new TIntermSymbol(&instanceVar)}};
65 return PreResult::Multi(std::begin(replacements), std::end(replacements));
66 }
67 else
68 {
69 ASSERT(type.getQualifier() == TQualifier::EvqUniform);
70
71 auto &structure =
72 *new TStructure(&mSymbolTable, interfaceBlock->name(),
73 &interfaceBlock->fields(), interfaceBlock->symbolType());
74 auto &structVar = CreateStructTypeVariable(mSymbolTable, structure);
75 auto &instanceVar =
76 CreateInstanceVariable(mSymbolTable, structure, Name(var),
77 TQualifier::EvqBuffer, &type.getArraySizes());
78
79 mInstanceMap[&var] = &instanceVar;
80
81 TIntermNode *replacements[] = {
82 new TIntermDeclaration{new TIntermSymbol(&structVar)},
83 new TIntermDeclaration{new TIntermSymbol(&instanceVar)}};
84 return PreResult::Multi(std::begin(replacements), std::end(replacements));
85 }
86 }
87 }
88
89 return {declNode, VisitBits::Both};
90 }
91
92 PreResult visitSymbolPre(TIntermSymbol &symbolNode) override
93 {
94 const TVariable &var = symbolNode.variable();
95 {
96 auto it = mInstanceMap.find(&var);
97 if (it != mInstanceMap.end())
98 {
99 return *new TIntermSymbol(it->second);
100 }
101 }
102 if (const TInterfaceBlock *ib = var.getType().getInterfaceBlock())
103 {
104 auto it = mLiftedMap.find(ib);
105 if (it != mLiftedMap.end())
106 {
107 return AccessField(*(it->second), var.name());
108 }
109 }
110 return symbolNode;
111 }
112};
113
114} // anonymous namespace
115
116////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
117
118bool sh::ReduceInterfaceBlocks(TCompiler &compiler, TIntermBlock &root, IdGen & idGen)
119{
120 Reducer reducer(compiler, idGen);
121 if (!reducer.rebuildRoot(root))
122 {
123 return false;
124 }
125
126 if (!SeparateDeclarations(&compiler, &root))
127 {
128 return false;
129 }
130
131 return true;
132}
